# Inspection phases to execute (space-separated list).
#
# Phases are executed once per protocol during diagnostic inspection.
# Each phase outputs diagnostic information about the current VPN state.
#
# Built-in phases:
#   firewall - Show PF rules, tables (vpn_dns, vpn_remotes), DNS/Remote IPs
#   vpn      - Show interface status, process info, configuration
#   dns      - Show DNS server, resolv.conf, resolvconf helper status
#
# Phase scripts location:
#   ${VPN_SWITCH_BASE}/.include/phase/${protocol}/inspect/${phase}.sh
#
# Unlike connect/disconnect phases which generate executable scripts,
# inspect phases output diagnostic information for troubleshooting.
#
# Usage:
#   - Executed by: vpn-switch phases inspect
#   - Each phase shows current state (not historical)
#   - Customize by editing .env/local/VPN_SWITCH_PHASES_INSPECT
#
